** {{tbox|You search the crate but find nothing.}}
** {{tact|end}}

==Showing the Generals different goblin armours==
===Orange-painted Goblin Armour===
* {{tcond|If the player uses a regular or non-orange painted goblin armour on one of the generals:}}
** '''Player:''' What do you think of this colour?
** '''General Bentnoze:''' That wrong colour.
** '''General Wartface:''' We tell you get orange armour.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the player uses orange dye on the goblin mail:}}
** {{mes|You dye the goblin mail orange.}}
** {{tact|receives=[[orange goblin mail]]}}
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the player uses orange-painted goblin armour on one of the generals:}}
** '''Player:''' I have some orange armour here.
** {{qact|A cutscene begins with the Generals fetching Grubfoot...}}
** '''General Wartface:''' Grubfoot!
** '''Grubfoot:''' Yes General Wartface?
** '''General Wartface:''' Put on this armour!
** {{qact|Grubfoot goes into the changing room with orange-painted goblin mail.}}
** '''Grubfoot:''' What do you think?
** '''General Wartface:''' No I don't like that much.
** '''General Bentnoze:''' It clashes with skin colour.
** '''General Wartface:''' We need darker colour, like blue.
** '''General Bentnoze:''' Yeah blue might be good.
** '''General Wartface:''' Human! Get us blue armour!
** {{qact|The cutscene ends.}}
** {{tact|end}}

===Blue-painted Goblin Armour===
* {{tcond|If the player uses a regular or non-blue painted goblin armour on one of the generals:}}
** '''Player:''' What do you think of this colour?
** '''General Bentnoze:''' That wrong colour.
** '''General Wartface:''' We tell you get blue armour.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the player uses blue dye on the goblin mail:}}
** {{mes|You dye the goblin mail blue.}}
** {{tact|receives=[[blue goblin mail]]}}
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the player uses blue-painted goblin armour on one of the generals:}}
** '''Player:''' I have some blue armour here.
** {{qact|Another cutscene begins with Grubfoot still wearing the orange armour.}}
** '''General Wartface:''' Grubfoot!
** '''Grubfoot:''' Yes General Wartface?
** '''General Wartface:''' Put on this armour!
** {{qact|Grubfoot goes into the changing room, switching his orange armour to blue armour.}}
